foia:ProcessedRequestSection.foia:FootnoteText: The Department of Education went through a reorganization in FY19. The following components were dissolved: OCFO-CAM, OCFO, ODS, OII, OM, and OM-OCPO. The following components were created: Exec Sec, OFO, and OFO-CAM. The Department of Education adjusted the number of requests pending at the start of the Fiscal Year accordingly. In addition, after reviewing its database, the Department of Education adjusted the number of requests pending at the start of the Fiscal Year for the following components: FSA, M, OCIO, OCO, OCR, Boston, New York, Dallas, Kansas City, OESE, OGC, OIG, OCLA, OPE, OPEPD, OS, OSERS, and OUS.
